	//   - product_certifications: Compliance badges (UL, CE, ISO, etc.)
	//   - product_downloads: Datasheets, manuals, CAD files, etc.
	//
	// Product status values: "published", "draft", "archived"
	// Features:
	//   - Multi-status workflow (draft/published/archived)
